Agarin Sorting 

We can sort the array of object like this

let arr = [
  {
    name: "Ankit",
    roll: 2,
  },
  {
    name: "Sonu",
    roll: 1,
  },
  {
    name: "Aankit",
    roll: 5,
  },
  {
    name: "Rohan",
    roll: 2,
  },
];

arr.sort((a, b) => (a.name > b.name ? 1 : -1));

console.log(arr);






















